channel.title: Garbled
channel.description: Podcast from the band Old Garbo featuring music, never heard before demos and live sessions together with insight into their music methodology and side-projects.

item.title: Garbled Issue 01: Under the Influence
item.description: In this first issue Russell Prothero, vocalist and guitarist with the band Old Garbo, talks about the song Under the Influence and plays the original demo which segues into the final album version.
item.author: oldgarbo@razoola.plus.com

item.title: Garbled Issue 02: Flown
item.description: In this second issue Russell Prothero, vocalist and guitarist with the band Old Garbo, talks about the development of the song Flown and plays the original demo which segues into the final album version.
item.author: oldgarbo@razoola.plus.com
